<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186100>
    bibo:endPage "57" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "45" ;
    bibo:volume "2022" ;
    dc:creator "Bartels, Paul J.; Pilato, Giovanni; Lisi, Oscar; Nelson, Diane R." ;
    dc:date "2009" ;
    dc:title "Macrobiotus (Eutardigrada, Macrobiotidae) from the Great Smoky Mountains National Park, Tennessee / North Carolina, USA (North America): two new species and six new records" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186104>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186105>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186106>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186107> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186104>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Macrobiotus halei sp. nov. (holotype). A, detail of the cuticular ornamentation (arrow). B, detail of the ornamentation on a leg where small tubercles and very small dots are visible. C, buccal-pharyngeal apparatus. D, claws of the third pair of legs. E, claws of the fourth pair of legs. (Scale bars = 10.0 µm)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/186104/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186105>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Macrobiotus halei sp. nov. A, egg. B, reticular design on the egg processes. C, ornamentation of the egg areolae. (Scale bars = 10.0 µm)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/186105/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186106>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. A, buccal-pharyngeal apparatus of Macrobiotus vanescens. B, claws of Macrobiotus priviterae. C, egg of Macrobiotus danielisae. D, egg of Macrobiotus lorenae. (Scale bars = 10.0 µm)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/186106/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186107>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. A, claws on the second and third pairs of legs of Macrobiotus gerlachae. B, egg of Macrobiotus gerlachae. C, claws on the first and second pairs of legs of Macrobiotus corgatensis. D, egg of Macrobiotus corgatensis. (Scale bars = 10.0 µm)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/186107/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

